{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "——第四周的早晨。\n和龙姐的治疗已经过了一个月。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（虽然还债还遥遥无期，但龙姐每周都会来……）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（多亏了利息宽限才勉强撑住……只要客人再多起来……！）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "triggerWeeklySettlement": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（……果然还是很紧张。得赶紧有新客人来才行……）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "哟。今天也来了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "smile",
      "text": "龙姐！一直以来谢谢您。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "嗯，你的治疗……说实话，让人上瘾。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "text": "诶？真的吗！？",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "smile",
      "text": "嗯。上周下班后肩膀也很轻松。平时应该会头痛的，结果完全没有。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "smile",
      "text": "太好了！看来治疗在起效。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "所以啊，我会推荐给组里的人。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "还有，我也可以给客户介绍你。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "smile",
      "text": "真的吗！？那太感谢了！",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（太好了！新客人要来了……！……等等，组里的人和龙姐的客户……）"
    },
     {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（全都是男的吧！唉……要是能来个巨乳美少女就好了……）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "不过呢，是我介绍的客人。给我好好做治疗。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "是、是的！当然！",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "说起今天的事。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "最近一直在应酬喝酒……肚子那一带感觉很沉重。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "肚子沉重吗。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "案头工作也很多，不怎么运动。总觉得胀胀的。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "原来如此……那今天试试仰卧治疗吧。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "alert",
      "text": "仰卧？跟之前不一样？",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "是的。仰卧的话可以好好针对腹部肌肉和内脏进行调理。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "改善腹部血液循环的话，消化系统的状态也会调整好。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……嗯。行吧，有效的话就试试。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "choice_massage4",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "腹部胀气放着不管可不好。",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "应酬多的话一定很辛苦吧",
          "trustDelta": 2,
          "developDelta": 0,
          "next": "sympathy_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "我来做调理内脏的治疗",
          "trustDelta": 1,
          "developDelta": 1,
          "next": "medical_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "请让我直接看看您的肚子",
          "trustDelta": 0,
          "developDelta": 2,
          "next": "lift_path"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "sympathy_path",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "作为社长，应酬和酒局之类的，很难推掉吧。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……嗯，就是这样。要管理组织就少不了交际。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "身体承受了那么多负担，我会好好帮您调理的。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "smile",
      "text": "……还不错。拜托了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png",
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "medical_path",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "有一种调理内脏功能的特殊手法。不过刺激可能会比较强。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "刺激强？嗯，有效的话就行。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "通过刺激腹部穴位来激活消化系统的功能。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……嗯。你好好做。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png",
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "lift_path",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "能把衣服撩起来让我直接看看肚子的状况吗？",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "alert",
      "text": "……啊？让我露肚子？",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "是的。视诊也很重要。要确认胀气之类的状况，直接看是最可靠的。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……嗯，既然是诊察的话。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "（龙姐自己撩起了衣服。）",
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_belly_show"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "……只是看哦？不准碰奇怪的地方。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png",
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_belly_show"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（……随着呼吸，柔软的肚子微微上下起伏……）",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_belly_show"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（微微泛着汗光……紧致的肚脐和下面的线条好美……）",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_belly_show"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（而且，再往上掀一点的话……）",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_belly_show"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……那个，能再往上掀一点点吗？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "……这样？",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（哦哦……看到胸罩了……！糟糕……）",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_belly_show"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "……喂！你刚才在看哪里！？",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png",
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_belly_show"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "alert",
      "text": "对、对不起！我只是在确认……！",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_belly_show"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……怎么样？",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "确实有些胀气。今天的治疗我会好好帮您放松的。",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "change_clothes",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "那么，请换上治疗用的衣服。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "嗯，知道了。……都第四次了，已经习惯了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "（龙姐熟练地开始换衣服……）",
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_changing"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "（……嗯，反正有效果。这点程度忍忍吧……）",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png",
      "cutInImage": "tatsu_changing"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "换好了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png",
      "outfit": "micro_bikini"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（看多少次都习惯不了，这身材……）",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "今天是仰卧治疗，请躺在床上。",
      "hideCharacter": true
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "……交给你了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "id": "massage_start",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "那么，开始治疗。"
    }
  ]
}
